data.title: PremierGarage of Central Oregon
data.meta_description: Learn more about PremierGarage of Central Oregon and our garage flooring and storage options.
data.text:
Allow me to introduce myself, I am Heather Gonzalez, the proud owner of PremierGarage of Central Oregon. I have lived in Oregon my entire life and have loved calling Bend, my home for more than twenty years. I feel distinguished to be a woman in a business, that specializes in custom home storage solutions. Since 2021, I have been operating every facet of my business. I am using the latest 3D design software to help homeowners customize their storage spaces. I take pride in getting to know my customers, so that I not only create spaces of their dreams, but also build relationships with my clients. I feel one of my strongest assets is building connections with my customers and community.

Hello,

I'm Kylie, a proud native of Bend, I've called this vibrant city home for my entire life, with a brief hiatus for four years while pursuing my passion for Business Management and Entrepreneurship at the University of Montana. I've gained invaluable knowledge that has fueled my dedication to fostering strong connections and making a mark in the business world.

Family and relationships are at the core of who I am, and I approach both life and work with a commitment to building lasting bonds. Whether it's delving into the intricacies of business or engaging in the diverse outdoor activities that Oregon generously offers, I find fulfillment in the constant exploration of the world around me.

In my professional life, I take pride in understanding my customers on a personal level, as I believe that genuine connections are the foundation of enduring relationships. With a passion for people and a background in business, I am excited to continue navigating the dynamic landscape of both my personal and professional endeavors here at PremierGarage of Central Oregon.
